This paper focuses on natural language processing (NLP) techniques to detect media bias in news articles. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with NLP and related topics. Additionally, the paper uses machine learning techniques, which suggests cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as another likely sub-category. The paper also deals with information retrieval and text classification, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) respectively. Lastly, the paper discusses the challenges of the task and future directions, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
